---
title: "US41 — Register / apply as expert"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>Expert Application Page (website)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SubmitExpertApplication
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SupabaseGateway + StorageGateway
  A->>B: fill application, attach credentials
  B->>C: submit(application)
  C->>G: upload expert_verification_documents
  C->>G: insert expert_profiles (status=pending)
  G-->>C: ok
  C-->>B: submitted
  B-->>A: "application under review"
